	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi literas ad vos in fine februarii; spero esse redditas.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">11. maii Bullingeri et <persName type="auto_name">Lavateri</persName> literas accepi, tuas vero, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gwalthere</persName>, 18. eiusdem mensis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Regina <placeName type="auto_name">Scotiae</placeName> e carcere evasit circa idem tempus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cruentum subito commissum est proelium inter papistas reginae amicos et protestantes regis fautores.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Illa, cum bellum ferveret, in colle celeri equo innsidens omnia oculis lustrabat; sed cum tandem videret victoriam cessisse d. Iacobo et suis, aufugit cum paucis in Angliam; maluit enim se <persName type="auto_name">Anglis</persName> committere quam suis Scotis, et credo tutius fuisse.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Agit iam <persName type="auto_name">Carleoli</persName>, in loco satis munito, brevi in medio Angliae commoratura, ut audio.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">13. iulii d. <persName type="auto_name">Gulielmus Turnerus</persName>, medicus bonus et vir optimus, <persName type="auto_name">Londini</persName> obiit; <persName type="auto_name">Leverus</persName> in eius funere est concionatus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi unicas has ad vos literas et breves quidem; dubito enim, utrum hae in tantis rerum tumultibus ad vestras manus sint perventurae, quare plures in praesentia scribere nolui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutate meo nomine amicos meos omnes et praecipue d. <persName ref="p2827" cert="high">Simlerum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Lavaterum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Wolphium</persName>, <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Wickium</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Vonlichium</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Zvinglium</persName> etc.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene valete.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Raptim <placeName ref="l299" cert="high">Ludhamiae</placeName> 4. augusti 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vester quantus quantus est <persName type="auto_name">Ioannes P[arkhurstus</persName>], <placeName type="auto_name">N[ordovicensis]</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Doctissimis viris et integerrimis amicis d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Rod[olpho] Gwalthero</persName> et d. Henrico Bullingero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
